👾💖 Welcome to @Norvina's cyber city! Follow @Norvina through this futuristic, imaginative world to find out all the personal details that went into "The Lilac Palette's" creation and campaign. From an homage to Dada (Norvina's grandma) to the formulas behind the shades and more!
